nodes.name: Data Architecture for Performance
nodes.description: Waiting looong minutes for a query to run or a report to show is a horrible thing. And a great way to get distracted from the task at hand.

nodes.name: Data Cleaning, Transformation & Integration
nodes.description: Want to make better decisions? It all starts with data quality. But what does data quality mean ? We’ ll help you figure it out.

nodes.name: Data Enrichment
nodes.description: You have finally built that awesome and clean data warehouse and filled it with internal data.

nodes.name: Statistics and Forecasting
nodes.description: Stuck in Analysis Paralysis? We’ ve seen it before. In this day and age, everyone brings data to the table… Somehow decision making seems more complicated than ever.

nodes.name: Governance & Change Management
nodes.description: You are getting traction with your teams, analysts are deploying good analytics and business users are getting onboard. How can you help your data culture to grow, while in the meantime making sure data is used correctly and securely?
